description:
First in the news: AdventHealth sends medicine to Ukraine to help those suffering from the aftermath of war.

Hope Media Colombia Center produced the first-of-its-kind children's animated series focused on stewardship. This project was launched by the Children and Adolescent Ministries in North Colombia to encourage children to be faithful stewards of Jesus.

“Encounter”, the Christian drama series, produced by Hope Media Europe starts this July. Its worldwide release is available in English, German, French, Portuguese, Spanish, Romanian, and Bulgarian.
